/* ### FLEX or FLEX BOX

- flexbox is a one-dimensional layout system (row(horizontal) , column (vertical))

1. understand the two-axis
   |
   |
   |
   cross axis
   ------main -------- axis --->
   |
   |
   |

flex properties

### parent properties

    - display  (block)
        -flex

- flex-direction (row) - column
  -row
  -column-reverse
  -row-reverse
- flex-wrap (nowrap) - wrap - no wrap
  -wrap-reverse
  -justified-content ( row -main axis) (column- main axis) - flex-start
  -flex-end
  -center
  -space-between
  -space-around
  -space-evenly
  -align-items (stretch -cross axis (column)) ( single row or cloumn) - flex-start
  -flex-end
  -center
  -align-content ( you need to have multiple row or column) - -flex-start
  -flex-end
  -center
  -space-between
  -space-around
  -space-evenly

  ## child properties

  - order
  - flex-grow
  - flex-shrink
  - flex-basis */